  <summary date="2021-09-12T18:48:22Z" status="Introduced in House">Menstrual Products Right To Know Act of 2019

This bill prohibits the sale of a menstrual product, such as a menstrual cup, menstrual pad, tampon, or therapeutic vaginal douche apparatus, unless its labeling includes a list of ingredients.</summary>
